snippet.title: Metroid Father Hunt NCFC 2013 Trailer
snippet.description: Short and sweet trailer made for the Nintendo Community Fangame Convention. Song is "Heart: Attack" by Neon Indian, and is not featured in the game. No copyright infringement intended.
